<li id="cite_note-Rogers5-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Rogers5_1-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Rogers5_1-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"/><cite id="CITEREFRogers2003" class="citation book cs1">Rogers, Everett (16 August 2003). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=9U1K5LjUOwEC"><i>Diffusion of Innovations, 5th Edition</i></a>. Simon and Schuster. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-7432-5823-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-7432-5823-4"><bdi>978-0-7432-5823-4</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Diffusion+of+Innovations%2C+5th+Edition&amp;rft.pub=Simon+and+Schuster&amp;rft.date=2003-08-16&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-7432-5823-4&amp;rft.aulast=Rogers&amp;rft.aufirst=Everett&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D9U1K5LjUOwEC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADiffusion+of+innovations" class="Z3988"></span></span>
